{"tid":270083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳來港 大屋搬細屋","createTime":"2017-06-04T06:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T08:18:14.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8eb9bf55bf9cce3e3a7658d73d79d8ae8318e1e5","tid":270083,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:01:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170604/00176_011.html?pubdate=20170604\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170604%2F00176_011.html%3Fpubdate%3D20170604&d=FWGQGMRI8%2BR9BXZI3QvkeZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=6da94680\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170604/00176_011.html?pubdate=20170604</a><br />\n <br />\n來自深圳的譚太表示，兒子讀幼兒班和低班時，每天花約一小時上學。去年擔心「跨境學童專用校網」會令兒子被派往偏遠學校，以月租四千元在上水租住一個細單位，面積僅及內地居所十分之一。幸兒子成功獲派第一志願，雖住得勉強，但很值得，會回內地與家人食飯慶祝。"},{"pid":"c698f1de39b66223a47a7a1209d4396b18ecb063","tid":270083,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:09:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f2d805722b0938eb1a47fc592d548505b7c586","tid":270083,"uid":54576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:10:20.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e445d6ed4015a68bde7c27b9119310adbd39ed","tid":270083,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:18:14.000Z","msg":"香港教育國際化=收大陸學生=國與國關係？"}]}